{# Description: Raw copy/paste Jinja monitor template for Spectra LS P5-S03 lighting-domain gate-prep and run-window validation feedback. #}
{# Version: 2026.04.21.2 #}
{# Last updated: 2026-04-21 #}

{# =========================
  P5-S03 Lighting Functionality Monitor (gate-prep safe)
  Purpose: fast live signal for lighting-domain readiness during bounded P5-S03 windows.
  Usage:
    1) Paste/run in Developer Tools -> Template.
    2) Capture output for pre-window / in-window / post-window records.
  ========================= #}

{% set s_target_primary = 'sensor.shadow_active_target' %}
{% set s_target_fallback = 'sensor.spectra_ls_shadow_active_target' %}
{% set primary_has_attrs = state_attr(s_target_primary, 'route_trace') is not none or state_attr(s_target_primary, 'captured_at') is not none %}
{% set fallback_has_attrs = state_attr(s_target_fallback, 'route_trace') is not none or state_attr(s_target_fallback, 'captured_at') is not none %}
{% set s_target = s_target_primary if primary_has_attrs else (s_target_fallback if fallback_has_attrs else s_target_primary) %}

{% set route_trace = state_attr(s_target, 'route_trace') or {} %}
{% set contract = state_attr(s_target, 'contract_validation') or {} %}
{% set write_controls = state_attr(s_target, 'write_controls') or {} %}
{% set unresolved = state_attr(s_target, 'unresolved_sources') or [] %}
{% set mismatches = state_attr(s_target, 'mismatches') or [] %}

{% set authority_mode = write_controls.authority_mode if write_controls is mapping and write_controls.authority_mode is defined else 'missing' %}
{% set route_decision = route_trace.decision if route_trace is mapping and route_trace.decision is defined else '' %}
{% set contract_valid = contract.valid if contract is mapping and contract.valid is defined else false %}
{% set missing_required = contract.missing_required if contract is mapping and contract.missing_required is defined else [] %}
{% set unresolved_required = contract.unresolved_required if contract is mapping and contract.unresolved_required is defined else [] %}

{% set room = states('input_select.control_board_room') %}
{% set target = states('input_select.control_board_target') %}
{% set target_entity = states('sensor.control_board_target_entity_id') %}
{% set room_on = states('binary_sensor.control_board_room_on') %}
{% set target_on = states('binary_sensor.control_board_target_on') %}

{% set room_options_raw = states('sensor.control_board_room_options') %}
{% set target_options_raw = states('sensor.control_board_target_options') %}
{% set room_options = (room_options_raw | trim | from_json(default=[])) if (room_options_raw is string and (room_options_raw | trim)[0:1] == '[') else [] %}
{% set target_options = (target_options_raw | trim | from_json(default=[])) if (target_options_raw is string and (target_options_raw | trim)[0:1] == '[') else [] %}

{% set room_selected_valid = room not in ['', 'unknown', 'unavailable', 'none', none] and (room_options | length) > 0 and room in room_options %}
{% set target_selected_valid = target not in ['', 'unknown', 'unavailable', 'none', none] and (target_options | length) > 0 and target in target_options %}
{% set target_entity_valid = (target == 'All') or (target_entity not in ['', 'unknown', 'unavailable', 'none', none]) %}
{% set selector_options_ready = (room_options | length) > 0 and (target_options | length) > 0 %}

{% set captured_at = state_attr(s_target, 'captured_at') | default('', true) %}
{% set captured_ts = as_timestamp(captured_at) if captured_at not in ['', 'unknown', 'unavailable', 'none', none] else none %}
{% set age_s = (as_timestamp(now()) - captured_ts) if captured_ts is not none else none %}
{% set control_snapshot_fresh = age_s is not none and age_s <= 300 %}

{% set status = 'PASS' %}
{% if authority_mode != 'legacy' %}
  {% set status = 'WARN' %}
{% endif %}
{% if not contract_valid or (missing_required | length) > 0 or (unresolved_required | length) > 0 %}
  {% set status = 'FAIL' %}
{% elif not selector_options_ready or not room_selected_valid or not target_selected_valid or not target_entity_valid or (unresolved | length) > 0 or (mismatches | length) > 0 %}
  {% set status = 'WARN' %}
{% endif %}

{% set readiness = 'NOT_READY' %}
{% if contract_valid and (missing_required | length) == 0 and (unresolved_required | length) == 0 and selector_options_ready and room_selected_valid and target_selected_valid and target_entity_valid and authority_mode == 'legacy' %}
  {% set readiness = 'READY' %}
{% elif not contract_valid or (missing_required | length) > 0 or (unresolved_required | length) > 0 %}
  {% set readiness = 'BLOCKED' %}
{% elif authority_mode != 'legacy' or not selector_options_ready or not room_selected_valid or not target_selected_valid or not target_entity_valid %}
  {% set readiness = 'CAUTION' %}
{% endif %}

### P5-S03 Lighting Functionality Monitor (`spectra_ls`)
- Status: **{{ status }}**
- Lighting readiness: **{{ readiness }}**
- Timestamp: **{{ now() }}**

### Authority + route baseline
- `write_controls.authority_mode`: **{{ authority_mode }}**
- `route_trace.decision`: **{{ route_decision if route_decision != '' else 'n/a' }}**

### Contract gate
- `contract_validation.valid`: **{{ contract_valid }}**
- `contract_validation.missing_required`: **{{ missing_required | length }}**
- `contract_validation.unresolved_required`: **{{ unresolved_required | length }}**

### Lighting selector gate
- `input_select.control_board_room`: **{{ room }}**
- `input_select.control_board_target`: **{{ target }}**
- `sensor.control_board_target_entity_id`: **{{ target_entity if target_entity not in ['', none] else 'n/a' }}**
- `sensor.control_board_room_options` count: **{{ room_options | length }}**
- `sensor.control_board_target_options` count: **{{ target_options | length }}**
- Selector options ready: **{{ selector_options_ready }}**
- Room selected valid: **{{ room_selected_valid }}**
- Target selected valid: **{{ target_selected_valid }}**
- Target entity valid: **{{ target_entity_valid }}**
- `binary_sensor.control_board_room_on`: **{{ room_on }}**
- `binary_sensor.control_board_target_on`: **{{ target_on }}**

### Parity + freshness
- `unresolved_sources`: **{{ unresolved | length }}**
- `mismatches`: **{{ mismatches | length }}**
- Control snapshot freshness (context only, <=300s): **{{ control_snapshot_fresh }}** (age_s={{ (age_s | round(1)) if age_s is not none else 'n/a' }})

{% if (missing_required | length) > 0 %}
Contract missing required entities:
{% for item in missing_required %}
- `{{ item }}`
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if (unresolved_required | length) > 0 %}
Contract unresolved required entities (present but unresolved):
{% for item in unresolved_required %}
- `{{ item }}`
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if (unresolved | length) > 0 %}
Unresolved parity sources:
{% for item in unresolved %}
- `{{ item }}`
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

{% if (mismatches | length) > 0 %}
Parity mismatches:
{% for item in mismatches %}
- `{{ item }}`
{% endfor %}
{% endif %}

### Quick interpretation
{% if readiness == 'READY' %}
- P5-S03 lighting lane is healthy for bounded-window evidence capture.
{% elif readiness == 'CAUTION' %}
- Lighting lane is partially healthy; normalize selector/authority posture before closeout interpretation.
{% elif readiness == 'BLOCKED' %}
- Lighting lane is blocked by contract failures; resolve FAIL conditions before continuing window execution.
{% else %}
- Lighting lane is not yet closeout-ready; capture additional bounded evidence and re-check.
{% endif %}

{% if not control_snapshot_fresh %}
- Note: control snapshot context is older than 300s. This is informational for P5-S03 and does not by itself downgrade lighting verdicts.
{% endif %}

### Suggested refresh actions
- Re-render this monitor before and after bounded lighting interactions.
- Keep `authority_mode=legacy` for gate-prep captures.
- If selector options are stale/missing, allow room/target sync automations to settle and rerender.
- Treat control snapshot age as context only; classify P5-S03 verdict from authority + contract + selector + parity signals.
